<h1><a href="<:url "articles/handle-a-fatal-error/":>">Handle a fatal error</a></h1>

<p>We’d love to catch and handle fatal errors in our code.
But that doesn’t seem possible!
After all, a fatal error is <i>fatal</i>—isn’t it?
And, yet, Lens does it.
Handle fatal errors with a technique straight out of Lens!</p>
